Package: jdPackages
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-02-24
Title: Personal R Project Scaffolding Tools
Authors@R: person("Joshua", "Preston", email = "joshua.preston@emory.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9834-3017"))
Description: Provides repo_template(), a function that scaffolds a complete,
    reproducible R analysis project following a consistent personal style.
    Creates directory structure, configuration files, renv setup, pipeline
    scripts, utility stubs, Docker templates, and GitHub Copilot instructions
    in one command.
